metadata.name: I'm falling for you
metadata.description:
My first try to create NFT of animation with original music!
Drowning in love to the point of suffocation,
a slightly  sad but beautiful love story.
 
All bidders will receive a NFT as a token of appreciation.
This is my first time to give NFT to all bidders, so I apologize if this causes any problem.
